## Medical Information
Headaches are a common condition that can be caused by various factors.
Common types of headaches include:
- Tension headaches (caused by muscle strain)
- Migraines (often associated with sensitivity to light and sound)
- Cluster headaches (severe pain around one eye)
- Sinus headaches (related to sinus inflammation)

Treatment options may include:
1. Over-the-counter pain medication
2. Rest and hydration
3. Stress management
4. Consultation with a healthcare provider for persistent symptoms
